1.update your ec2 instance
  sudo yum update

2.install docker on your instance
  sudo yum install docker

3.start docker on your instance
  sudo service docker start

4.enable docker on yor instance
  sudo systemctl enable docker

5.To know your docker status
  sudo service docker status

6.add your ec2 user to the docker group
  sudo usermod -a -G docker ec2-user

7.reboot your ec2 instance
  sudo reboot

8.after this step your ec2 will get disconnected you will need to reconnect it
